jasima.core.simulation.arrivalprocess

类 ArrivalsStationary

  • java.lang.Object

  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class ArrivalsStationary
extends ArrivalProcess
    This class can be used to create a stationary arrival process which can be described by a certain sequence of inter-arrival times (using, e.g., DblDistribution).
    作者:
    Torsten Hildebrandt, 2012-08-07
    另请参阅:
    DblStream, 序列化表格
